<p><a name="Books_based_upon_interviews_with_Campbell" id="Books_based_upon_interviews_with_Campbell"></a></p>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Monomyth&amp;action=edit&amp;section=33" title="Edit section: Books based upon interviews with Campbell">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Books based upon interviews with Campbell</span></h3>
<div class="references-small" style="margin-left:1.5em;">
<ul>
<li><i>The Hero's Journey: Joseph Campbell on his Life and Work.</i> Edited and with an Introduction by Phil Cousineau. Forward by Stuart L. Brown, Executive Editor. New York: Harper and Row, 1990.</li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/The_Power_of_Myth" title="The Power of Myth">The Power of Myth</a></i> (with <a href="/wiki/Bill_Moyers" title="Bill Moyers">Bill Moyers</a> and <a href="/wiki/Betty_Sue_Flowers" title="Betty Sue Flowers">Betty Sue Flowers</a>, ed.), 1988</li>
</ul>
